{"tid":706983,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［古裝女神大戰］迪麗熱巴 vs 周秀娜","createTime":"2018-06-18T10:16:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T08:32:56.000Z","uid":41351,"like":77,"dislike":128,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"7cfac7d5d20bf22b58635fe9626769648a384c4b","tid":706983,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T10:16:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/18/181421_9084fa5bf3e6e99ba12acffd7879541f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F18%2F181421_9084fa5bf3e6e99ba12acffd7879541f.png&h=7f0a0646&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無綫重頭劇《宮心計2深宮計》播出兩周，萬眾期待的周秀娜終以純熙身份亮相，首次拍攝古裝劇集的周秀娜無論係初次登場的俠女純熙姑娘、到冊封為二品昭儀後的造型都可以話係既討好又充滿新鮮感，特別係侍寢一幕，一襲紅衣加上嬌憨嫵媚的模樣，足以讓人驚豔。周秀娜之前訪問時就話過一直都對宮鬥劇十分感興趣，奈何唔少導演都認為她外表時裝味重，所以一直與古裝劇無緣，但經過《深宮計》後，相信唔少導演都會改觀。雖然周秀娜因所屬嘅公司正在與TVB打官司而未能參與《深宮計》宣傳，但不少網友對她的演出抑或古裝扮相都十分期待。<br />\n<br />\n今次投票因香港01說周秀娜古裝同熱巴有得而來<br />\n<br />\n正評：熱巴<br />\n負評： 周秀娜<br />\n大家覺得邊個靚d"},{"pid":"b0aa9cc9665f73fe09878ebda7ff386bff250ff9","tid":706983,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T10:17:48.000Z","msg":"娜姐"},{"pid":"951940cea670722c6ee3cb37882d2c73cee9a9f2","tid":706983,"uid":41351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T10:19:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/18/181913_8e22ac90b2277ae5ffe3b56e183d7529.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F18%2F181913_8e22ac90b2277ae5ffe3b56e183d7529.png&h=992dce27&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/18/181915_96e023be422337e9e2dce7bf2b0eb86e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F18%2F181915_96e023be422337e9e2dce7bf2b0eb86e.png&h=4e9b564a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/18/181916_96e023be422337e9e2dce7bf2b0eb86e.p